sections.name: PATIENT CONSENT TO COLLECT & DISCLOSE INFORMATION

fields.label: acknowledge that a Health Assessment will be conducted by AMC360 during the time of my appointment. This assessment will be conducted by an a Health Professional in consultation with a General Practitioner (GP).

groups.label: with multimedia devices being used throughout my Medical

Assessment. This may include the use of photography and videos to assist in the Quality of Health Assessments. This information will be held by AMC360 and will not be passed on to any personal or third Party without prior consent from the patient.

fields.label: I acknowledge that I am an Aboriginal or Torres Strait Islander Person and give permission for my Health Assessment to be conducted. I give permission for AMC360 to collect personal information about myself/my child as part of the Health Assessment to develop an individualised Health Care Plan and to provide Quality Health Care. Such Information may include:

groups.label: I give permission for AMC360 to release my/my child’s confidential information regarding any diagnostic testing, pathology reports, imaging, referrals and my Health Care Plan to the General Practitioner, Specialists and other Allied Health Professionals if required. I am aware that my health data may be recorded for statistical analysis and research purposes whilst remaining confidential.

You are entitled to access your own health records at any time convenient to both yourself and the practice. Written  and signed consent may be required. Where you disagree with the accuracy of the information recorded please discuss  this with your doctor as you are entitled to have your corrections included in your file.
I declare that the information that is set out through questionnaires and in the Health Assessment are truthful and that there are no misleading answers or omissions.
to AMC360 and its staff to take, photographs, digital images and/ or audio and/ or video footage (the images) for the purposes of my Health Assessment.

AMC360 and its staff will not to use any images in a way that would cause embarrassment or misrepresent the  intent of the Health Assessment or the individual. I understand that neither I/ My Child will be paid for giving this  permission and I hereby waive any claim that I or we may have or may have had for remuneration, residuals, royalties or any other payment in respect of use of the images.
Are there any aspects of your health that you are concerned about?
What would be a good outcome for you after completing the assessment?
